title: FK Vrapčište
text:
FK Vrapčište () is a <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club based in the village of <a href="Vrap%C4%8Di%C5%A1te">Vrapčište</a>, near <a href="Tetovo">Gostivar</a>, <a href="Republic%20of%20Macedonia">Republic of Macedonia</a>. They are currently competing in the <a href="Macedonian%20Third%20Football%20League">Macedonian Third League</a> (West Division).
History.
The club was founded in 1958.
It used the name FK Murgovec until 2011.
